	)
	(text "When not in frame, the previous\nPPU read address always looks\nlike $0000.  Since A13, A12 are\nlooking at range $2xxx instead\nof matches, $0xxx won't match\n$2xxx.  Therefore, scanlines\ndon't get detected when using\nPPUDATA to read from $0000\nduring v-blank."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 37.592 142.24 0)
		(effects
			(font
